name: Happy Holidays from The Noun Square!

metadata.name: Happy Holidays from The Noun Square! 1/969
metadata.description:
A special limited and free-to-claim edition for our TNS family, to thank you for all your support in 2022. Art by community artist Antruong (https://twitter.com/anufo204), commissioned by The Noun Square. One per wallet.

Have a Very Nounish Holiday, and a Noggly New Year!

properties.name: Happy Holidays from The Noun Square!
